  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Some of the items in the PM's media section are magical",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Prime Minister's Media Unit has lodged a complaint with the Koluppitiya Police Station that many items from the media section of Alarimalikai have been stolen.",
        "In addition, a complaint has been made that some other items including two laptops and one video camera have been stolen from the media section.",
        "It is also reported that after Ranil Wickremesinghe took office as Prime Minister, he did not go to Alari Palace, only a part of his media unit was operating in Alari Palace.",
        "In this situation, the media wing of the Prime Minister has reported that the said items disappeared only after the protesters entered Alari House on the 9th."
      ],
